title: FF (Marvel NOW) 001-007 (Up-to-date through May 15, 2013)
description:
Marvel NOW shows you the future, and it's fantastic!

In the Fantastic Four's absence, a hand-picked substitute squad -- Ant-Man, Medusa, She-Hulk and Miss Thing -- must guard Earth and the fledgling Future Foundation for four minutes.

What could go wrong?

------

Another interesting relaunch from the NOW! line, FF has teamed the new Fantastic Four writer Matt Fraction with the old X-Statix artist team of Michael Allred (pencils & inks) and his wife, Laura (colors). If you enjoy Allred's work, this is great. Give it a try, regardless!  --STF
